Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================MAIN========================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于复活了的沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誉为传说中的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法对它无效还会跟龙一样喷吐 这要咋整啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上它的目标居然还是塞伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Legacy 决战 塞伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请退避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Flare Seal{\r}\N炎咒封杀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝菲尔大人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开火开火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法…无效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的魔兽 沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我是谁也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们该知道的是自身的所为和报应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是千钧一发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算赶上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塞伦国的精英们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤员立即退避到后方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能站起来的人再一次施展力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你们的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是先退下比较好 丝菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高…高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追到这里来了吗 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不阻止你 谁来阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 不能让你为所欲为哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有光之剑 意志倒还真坚决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就试试是否能和传说中一样 打倒我沙那法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 先到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里就能做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说现在还不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了 迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想救的到底是些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊…虽然想这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里一路又是翔封界又是用跑的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是坐在人家头上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 看来总算赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维瑟大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这位大人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鲁比那加尔德王国特别搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监察官 附近的夫人们也好评不绝的维瑟·弗雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些先扔一边 快点联络塞伦王宫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是正事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿吃的来please
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我单刀直入地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比那加尔德王国乔康达公爵一手培育出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的魔兽沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直逼塞伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 在远方袭击我们的果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 居然是沙那法？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出突然虽是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来是没有怀疑的余地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑了那么远的路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好补充能量可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一路不停不歇地一直跑过来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你们跑了那么多路还真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营养涌入体内了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充满了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 丝菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才太混乱 都没好好打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不见了呢 丝菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你既身为巫女 同时也在军方救援部队帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我没做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚和我们作战的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是传说中的魔兽 沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说120年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把魔导都市赛拉格毁灭的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤的硬度在龙之上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神世界面的障壁也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有魔法都对牠无效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是夸大其辞吧 这个传说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 基本跟传说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是晕倒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那种东西会对塞伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个说来话长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 说起来普库塔在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比那加尔德王国要如何对此事件负责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是装作部分属下失控
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实为鲁比那加尔德王国的挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 请等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是一介公爵的失控
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鲁比那加尔德王国没有任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 还是应该先考虑我国的防御政策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先展开重装步兵部队 强化防御
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢 面对沙那法步兵能有何作为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该出动魔导部队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法对沙那法无效是众所周知的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让脆弱的魔导部队送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平日总是叫嚣着无敌的魔导部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种关键时刻就退缩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是互相推卸责任的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是合众人之力对抗沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇幻的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然由于某种原因而成了这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是塔夫拉西亚的正当王位继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普塞尔·库鲁巴·塔夫拉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉西亚的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那个国家在很多年前就覆灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 塔夫拉西亚现在也依然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是证明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助鲁比那加尔德王国的乔康达公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使魔兽沙那法复活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来也是我国同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想为此负责才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的魔兽沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是过去毁灭魔导都市赛拉格的强大怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再扩大灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位可以助我一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 但人类能对抗沙那法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能光靠我塞伦一国来和沙那法抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是先战略撤退 再和诸国商议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结成联合军 然后才能与之抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间做那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着时间推移 沙那法的破坏一直在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再让任何人受伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和塔夫拉西亚都没有任何力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不阻止沙那法不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个责任该由谁来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是国家的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人命关天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不阻止它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上所有人都会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我塞伦化为灰烬也在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在选错道路的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们将不得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普塞尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了塔夫拉西亚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对没能施以援手一事深感愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在讨伐沙那法一事上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国将倾尽全力相助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利欧尼路殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是菲利欧尼路王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是明理之人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是传说中的魔兽沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是即使举塞伦全军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没把握能够抗衡的对手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要合众人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会尽力相助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来又要把塞伦的命运托付给莉娜大人你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也重新拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我阻止沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她既然这么说了 就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是毫无根据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要正义在我们一方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利就是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是送上门来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你立刻命令王国军引导居民避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见沙那法的身影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 它就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 在空中只会被它狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道它会从哪发动袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就潜伏在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会突然从脚底跑出来啊呜一口吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么害怕的话你别跟来就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我维瑟·弗雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有将来龙去脉告诉附近太太们作为手信的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为这义务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝菲尔也要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时候请保护我哦 高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝菲尔能用治疗魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是战况不妙就得靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别藏着 快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜这种东西人就能得救的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为做这种事能改变什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要展示多少他人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界才会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是温柔的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为知道他人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人才能会有一瞬变得温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白银的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变得这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身体会变得更强大更完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这塞伦为粮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为人类是你的饵食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是沙那法真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会当你的饵食
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道要是吃了普库塔和莉娜的话会有多惨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会吃坏肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是那样倒还算幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那样就能打倒沙那法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙那法能够完全获得成为粮食的人的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万物之母 噩梦之王的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔康达应该也看见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了她的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会用挺有趣的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽不能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对其起源的知识有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的知识和力量以及性命 都是我自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也别想抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就尽你所有的力量挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要冷静地避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接近都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻举妄动会被逆袭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中就没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你可不能这么容易被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别看高里那德性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是世代传承光之剑一族的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是水母脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 高里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用魔法掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 有这个就以一当百了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记那只是复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用得太过会性命不保的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可顾不上这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地精道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通啊 高里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之起码在居民们都避难之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把它压制住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍太浅了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然光之剑有效那这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Astral Vine{\r}\N魔皇灵斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王结魔弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚 撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棘手的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去掩护高里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果用莉娜的那个魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个魔法的消耗很激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能忘记那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================ED========================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}{\pos(861,445)}{\fscx80\fs16}あめ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴れ渡る空から 落ちるとおり涙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴朗的空中落下雨泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}流れてゆく雲に 追いつけなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}漂浮的流云无从追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅立ちの先には 新しい出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅途前方是新的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}でも流されてるようで 落ち着かなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}但随波逐流的感觉令人不安
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}それでも この瞬間に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即便如此 这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全てが　終わる　訳じゃない そうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}并非一切都已结束 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あきれる程 悩み抜いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}摆脱那些琐碎的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出ない答え 今はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}未知的答案 现在已不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ほら本当は　あきらめていない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}看吧 其实你并没放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まだまだ行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}还能继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一緒に行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与我同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}覚悟決めてね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================NEXT========================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 Slayers Revolution也终于到了高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉沙那法就收工
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slayers Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misty 挥下的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我可要发飙咯！
